3. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to paris##2
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1  |   2    |    3     |  4   |  5   |   6    |
| City   | london | colone | berlin | rome | paris | boston |

