.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, action, sports, scientific, thriller, romance
1. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching action movies##2
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching action movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | action | sports | romance | scientific |

