2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing poker and the person playing bridge##2
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |
| Game   | whist | canasta | monopoly | bridge | scrabble | poker |

