.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-2-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, skateboard, taxi, ship, car, bus
1. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the train##2
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |    3    |    4    |    5    |   6   |
| Transport   | skateboard | train | bus | taxi | car | ship |

 